data.description: Featuring exceptional curb appeal and a great location is this gorgeous home in Prescott Oaks! The front of this home includes a widened driveway, a stone flowerbed, and a beautifully stained fence. As you enter the home, a grand open-concept floorplan invites you in and provides the perfect backdrop for hosting events with loved ones. The spacious kitchen boasts gorgeous countertops, intricate tile backsplash, an upgraded black faucet, fresh white cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Completing the downstairs area is a formal dining room adorned with a designer light fixture and an upgraded half bathroom. Upstairs is a peaceful haven with a secondary living space and four spacious bedrooms. Rejuvenate within the primary bedroom and modern en suite bathroom. The backyard is an exceptional getaway with plenty of grassy space to roam, an extended patio, and two beautiful trees. This home features proximity to Highway 1604 and has many excellent shopping and dining choices in the Alamo Ranch area. Begin the next chapter of your journey and make this dream home yours today!
